  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK272">
<l>vāṉuyar tōṟṟa mevaṉceyyun taṉṉeñcan</l>
<l>tāṉaṟi kuṟṟam paṭiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What avails an appearance (of sanctity) high as heaven, if his mind suffers (the indulgence) of conscious sin.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
